<p id="_a467da43-663b-a604-4bf2-fe0f7987d2d0">equivalent to</p>

<p id="_d75c8781-40ce-8936-b148-a8dc0f02d872"><stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
