    </mrow>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>ii(lambda) (""^199 "Hg"^"+") = 281568867.5919685 "unitsml(fm)"</asciimath></stem></p>

<p id="_090f19f5-5a1e-bf06-2bbe-50b3632fab10">with a relative uncertainty of <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
