        <mo>−</mo>
        <mn>15</mn>
      </mrow>
    </msup>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>1.9 xx 10^(-15)</asciimath></stem>.</p>

<p id="_5cce94b0-3418-b87f-f5b9-c1d578d80f0a">This radiation was already endorsed as a secondary representation of the definition of the second.</p>
</clause>

